Description: Apple Studio Display brightness indicator for wingpanel
 A native elementary OS wingpanel indicator that controls the brightness of an
 Apple Studio Display. It adds its own icon to the panel with a slider popover
 and scroll-to-adjust, and appears only while a Studio Display is connected.
 .
 Brightness is driven through the asdbctl command-line tool, which must be
 installed separately (https://github.com/juliuszint/asdbctl). This package
 ships the udev rule that grants the logged-in user access to the display's
 HID device without root.
